window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It all comes down to one final fight for the future of the Federation. Even without the Morgana in her head, Stephanie's attitude has become dark indeed.</p> <p>Now, she has decided the best way to stop a war is attack.</p> <p>Unfortunately, the Telorans have not arrived, and will likely miss this battle.</p> <p>Stephanie considers the cost in lives of those in cryo-storage and is willing to gamble the whole effort to save those who are still sleeping.</p> <p>Is it the best decision militarily? Probably not.</p> <p>But if she didn't, she wouldn't be the Witch of the Federation.</p> <p>It's the final book. Strap yourself in and let's get started.</p>"; 
